title: [2006] Heavy Heavy Low Low - Everything's Watched, Everyone's
description:
Everything&#039;s Watched, Everyone&#039;s Watching is the second full-length album from Californian experimental band Heavy Heavy Low Low. Contains eleven tracks (the bonus track is attatched to "Party Girls"), plus album artwork:

1. "This Is Really Testing the Patience I&#039;ve Never Had" - 0:33
2. "A, S, V, L, N" - 1:27
3. "Mall-Nutrition" - 1:55
4. "Are You Okay, Kiddo?" - 2:17
5. "I Forgot 2 and a Half Days" - 2:05
6. "Texas Chainsaw Mascer-uh" - 1:15
7. "Kids, Kids, Kids" - 1:43
8. "Buddy, You&#039;re Making No Sense" - 2:27
9. "There&#039;s a Bat" - 1:13
10. "Eating the Porridge and Killing the Bears" - 1:38
11. "Party Girls" (plus bonus track) - 5:37
